      <article class="post-78867 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-economics category-history category-uncategorized" id="post-78867">
  <header class="entry-header">

          <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2020/06/what-should-i-ask-nathan-nunn-twitter-version-of-this-query.html">What should I ask Nathan Nunn &#8212; Twitter version of this query</a></h2>
    
      <div class="byline">
        by&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="author"><a href="/about">Tyler Cowen</a></span>
        <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2020-06-30 21:14:39">June 30, 2020 at 9:14 pm </time>
                            in
          <ul class="entry-tags">
                                        <li class="tag" rel="tag"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/category/economics">Economics</a></li>
                                                      <li class="tag" rel="tag"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/category/history">History</a></li>
                                                              </ul><!-- /.entry-tags -->
                        </div><!-- /.byline -->
  </header><!-- /.entry-header -->
  <div class="entry-content">
    <div class="pf-content"><p>I will be doing a Conversation with him, MR readers <a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2020/06/what-should-i-ask-nathan-nunn.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">offered suggestions here</a>, I will tweet a request for queries, please leave them in the comments section of this post.  This post is only for people coming in from Twitter.</p>
</div>
  </div><!-- /.entry-content -->
